Aureline
========

Aureline is an independent proxy client shell. It is not an official project of
mihomo, Clash, MetaCubeX, clash-rs, meow, or Avalonia.

Project code owned by this repository is licensed under the Apache License 2.0.

Third-party components
----------------------

- Avalonia and .NET for Android/iOS are used for the application UI and platform
  bindings. See their upstream license notices.
- libclash is an in-repository native core wrapper around github.com/metacubex/mihomo.
  mihomo/libclash based release artifacts must comply with GPL-3.0.
- clash-rs is used by the Aureline.ClashRs.Android variant. Its base license is
  Apache-2.0, but its upstream NOTICE may require GPL-3.0 when GPL features are
  enabled.
- libmeow/meow-rs is used by the Aureline.Meow.Android variant and is MIT
  licensed upstream.

The application name "Aureline" and Chinese name "曜线" are project branding for
this repository only and should not be used to imply endorsement by upstream
native core projects.
